channel.title: How Do You Add Thieving Stall Questions? So No Auto Clickers
channel.description: Hey I was just wondering how do you add questions on project insanity, 317 server so that when u thieve u get questions randomly so that you cant auto click to get money? If you get the answer wrong you get teleported please help.

item.title: How Do You Add Thieving Stall Questions? So No Auto Clickers
item.dc:creator: @arham_4 arham 4
item.description:
@arham_4 wrote:

Fire capez:

I don’t have much experience in this department but there’s a mouse clicking packet that you could probably track, auto clickers aren’t sophisticated they take the same pattern usually, so you could check whether the mouse was moved by the same amount for 25 or so consecutive clicks and then spawn a random.

packet 130 or 102 (don’t count on it, I am talking Rom memory).
